        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Full cut-in installation for Beatrice basements, sized to meet Nebraska code for a legal bedroom. See our <a href="/egress-window-installation-lincoln/">egress window installation</a> process.</p>
